      "fields": {
        "remarks": "<format type=\"text/markdown\"><![CDATA[\n## Remarks\n\n`SKColorspacePrimariesCicp` enumerates the color primaries defined by the Coding-Independent Code Points (CICP) specification (ITU-T H.273 / ISO/IEC 23091-2). Use these values with <xref:SkiaSharp.SKColorSpace.CreateCicp*> to create a color space from standardized primaries.\n\nThis enumeration is a value type and does not require disposal.\n\n## Examples\n\n```csharp\nusing var colorSpace = SKColorSpace.CreateCicp(\n    SKColorspacePrimariesCicp.Rec709,\n    SKColorspaceTransferFnCicp.Rec709);\n```\n]]></format>",
        "remarksRequired": true,
        "summary": "Specifies color primaries as defined by the CICP (Coding-Independent Code Points) standard."
      },
      "docId": null,
      "memberType": "type"
    },
